translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,98,"Ingaba sasikhe sakho isixeko esasikhe sakholwa lwaza ukholo lwaso lwasisindisa ngaphandle kwabantu bakuloYûnus, abakholwayo, Saza Sasirhoxisa isohlwayo esingcungcuthekisayo phezu kwabo, esilihlazo kobu bomi beli hlabathi, eSabavumela ukuba babonwabele okwethutyana"
  10,99,"Ukanti ukuba iNkosi yakho Yayithandile, abo basemhlabeni ngesele bakholwa bonke, ingaba wena (Muhammad) uza kubanyanzela na abantu, bakholwe ngetshova"
  10,100,"Ayikokwamntu ukukholwa ngaphandle kwemvume ka- Allâh, yaye Yena Uza kuthoba ingqumbo yaKhe kwabo bangakhathaliyo"
  10,101,"Yithi: “Yabonani! Konke okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni (kokuka-Allâh)”. Kodwa akukho Vesi naMlumkisi ungaba luncedo kwabo bangakholwayo"
  10,102,"Ke kaloku ingaba kusekho nto abasayilindileyo iyenye ngaphandle (kwentshabalalo) enjengeemini zabantu abadlulayo ngaphambi kwabo? Yithi ke wena: “ Lindani kaloku nam oku kwam ndilindile kunye nabo balindileyo.”"
  10,103,Ke kaloku (ekugqibeleni) Samsindisa uMthunywa weThu kunye nabo bakholwayo! Kuyimfanelo enjalo ke kuThi ukusindisa amakholwa
  10,104,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Hini na bantu! Ukuba nineentandabuzo mayela neNkolo yam [i-Islam, (kwazini kakuhle)] ke okokuba mna andisokuze ndizinqule ezo zinto nizinqulayo nina ngaphandle koAllâh, kodwa mna ndiya kunqula uAllah ekunguYe Onenza nife, yaye mna ndiyalelwe ukuba ndibe ngomnye wamakholwa"
  10,105,"Ke kaloku wena (Muhammad) bhekisa ubuso bakho ngqo kwinkolo yobuHanîfa, ungaze ube ngomnye wabakhonzi bezithixo"
  10,106,"Ungabizi kwenye into ngaphandle koAllâh engayi kukunceda, ingazi kukonzakalisa nokonzakalisa kodwa ukuba ukhe wayenza into enjalo, inene wena uya kuba ngomnye wabalahlekelwa"